    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-04-14</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-04-29T19:04:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to revise the definition of certain small crude oil refiners eligible for the exemption from limitations applicable to the percentage depletion allowance for oil and gas wells to provide that such refiners will qualify for the exemption if their average daily refinery runs do not exceed 75,000 barrels (currently, 50,000 barrels). </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
